<!--XML file used to describe the runtime query handlers. 
*    data-sources : container of relevant data-source entities
*      name - optional and ignore
*      
*    data-source : the entity used to describe the source of data to query
*      name - unique name of the source of data
*      type - unique type given to distinguish this data-source from any other; NO WHITESPACE
*      delegateClassname - the name of the class that inherits from com.eureka.delegate.DatasourceBusinessDelegate
*                          and overloads the following methods
*                          1. public ISearchQueryResult query(ISearchQueryInput queryInput) throws ProcessingException
*                          2. public List<Field> getValidFields() throws ProcessingException
*                          3. public List<String> queryForAvailableFieldValues(ISearchQueryInput searchQueryInput)
*                          
*      fields : container of relevant field data entities for a given data-source
*        field - the entity used to describe a unique field of data required of the data-source to do its work.  this
*                likely includes connectivity parameters, configuration parameters, etc.. only has context for the 
*                data-source and likely the delegateClassName instance
*          name - unique name value of the field
*         displayName - the value to use when displaying the field
*         hideInList - whether to hide or show it when in a list/grid or not
-->          
                          
